text: Jack William Shutt (born 24 June 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut on 25 July 2019, for Yorkshire in the 2019 t20 Blast. He made his first-class debut on 1 August 2020, for Yorkshire in the Bob Willis Trophy. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Yorkshire cricketers Category:Cricketers from Barnsley Category:English cricketers of the 21st century
